{"synckey":1673274120,"updated":[{"bookId":"23784694","bookmarkId":"23784694_8_3286-3696","chapterUid":8,"markText":"1.你可以将钱藏在垫子下面（但这个计划有些迂腐）。2.你可以将钱存入银行或购买美国政府债券。这样保证获得收益，而且没有风险。[插图]3.你可以购买某些公司或其他机构销售的债券，这样能获得比银行或政府更高的利息，但你可能会面临亏损甚至失去你全部的投资，因此，你的回报必须能够弥补你所承担的风险才行。4.你可以用自己的钱干别的事。","range":"3305-3715","createTime":1559521288,"type":1},{"bookId":"23784694","bookmarkId":"23784694_8_1311-1362","chapterUid":8,"markText":"最重要的是要攒钱去买需要的或将来需要的东西，而不是浪费钱财买一个需要沿街追上三四分钟的巨大的气象气球。","range":"1330-1381","createTime":1559520982,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"第二章 最基本的四种投资渠道","chapterUid":8,"chapterIdx":8}],"book":{"bookId":"23784694","version":1077241279,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/55/YueWen_23784694/s_YueWen_23784694.jpg","title":"股市稳赚","author":"乔尔·格林布拉特","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K4OVStt6-o_3jsIB0Layx]","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#331400"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3a0f00"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#410700"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#462b10"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#4d2800"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#522500"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#5f4124"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#663f0e"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#6b3c00"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#753700"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#825725"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#8d5300"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#7b5a38"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#ab6c00"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#957352"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#a66e23"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#af8d6a"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#ba8a54"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#c2883d"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#ce8300"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#dea256"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#e69f3c"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ec9d13"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#e4c29b"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#f0bf85"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ffb735"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f3e0ca"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffd251"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#c2883d"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#dea256"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3EDE5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3EDE5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#271300"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#d2ac82","hsv":[31.31695801224527,38.4545382